@startuml sequence_self_register
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Participant Self-Registration (Happy Path)

actor Participant
participant "EntryPage" as EP
participant "Zod Schema" as ZOD
participant "API Client" as API
participant "Express API" as Server
participant "Registration\nService" as SVC
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

Participant -> EP: Scans QR → opens /enter
EP -> API: getActiveRaffle()
API -> Server: GET /api/public/active-raffle
Server --> API: 200 { raffle }
API --> EP: ActiveRafflePublic (accepting entries)
EP --> Participant: Show name form

Participant -> EP: Types "Alice", taps "Join Raffle"
EP -> ZOD: validate({ name: "Alice" })
ZOD --> EP: valid

EP -> API: registerParticipant("Alice")
API -> Server: POST /api/public/register\n{ name: "Alice" }

Server -> SVC: registerParticipant("Alice")
SVC -> DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION
SVC -> DB: SELECT raffle WHERE isActive
DB --> SVC: raffle (no draws yet)
SVC -> DB: CHECK duplicate name
DB --> SVC: no duplicate
SVC -> DB: INSERT participant
DB --> SVC: created
SVC -> DB: COMMIT
SVC --> Server: participant

Server --> API: 201 { participant }
API --> EP: success
EP --> Participant: "You're in! Good luck."

@enduml
